snippet.title: Solstice Chronicles: MIA [Nintendo Switch eShop] Features Trailer
snippet.description:
Solstice Chronicles: MIA is a sci-fi action shooter that launches on the Nintendo Switch eShop on 7th February.

It introduces smart mechanics and skills that give you multiple ways to tackle the challenge. With support for co-op in Story and Survival modes, there are lots of chances to destroy mutants!

Follow us on Twitter! https://twitter.com/CIRCLE_Ent
